    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织下调全球增长预测，警告风险加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/imf-lowers-global-growth-forecast-warns-of-increasing-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织下调了明年全球经济增长预测，并警告称，战争、贸易保护主义等风险正在加剧，但同时该组织也赞扬各国央行抑制了通胀，而没有让各国陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/imf-lowers-global-growth-forecast-warns-of-increasing-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
